If the following series is written in the reverse order, which number will be fourth to the right of the seventh number from the left?   </br> 7, 3, 9, 7, 0, 3, 8, 4, 6, 2, 1, 0, 5, 11, 13 </br> यदि  नीचे दी गई श्रंखला को उलटे क्रम में लिखा जाए, तो कौन सा अंक बायें से सातवें अंक के दायें से चौथा अंक होगा?   </br> 7, 3, 9, 7, 0, 3, 8, 4, 6, 2, 1, 0, 5, 11, 13
@0@5@9@11@1@The given series when written in the reserve order becomes: </br> 13, 11, 5, 0, 1, 2, 6, 4, 8, 3, 0, 7, 9, 3, 7 </br> Then 7th number from the left is 6. The 4th number to the right is 6 is 0.